      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://metaloom.io/docs/loom/artifacts/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Loom publishes JVM artifacts and container deployment assets separately.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sect1&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;_maven_artifacts&#34;&gt;Maven Artifacts&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;sectionbody&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&#34;../maven-artifacts/&#34;&gt;Maven Artifacts&lt;/a&gt; for the BOM and the primary client and shared model modules.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Authentication</title>
      <link>https://metaloom.io/docs/loom/authentication/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://metaloom.io/docs/loom/authentication/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;paragraph&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Loom uses JWT (JSON Web Token) bearer tokens for API authentication.&#xA;OAuth2 integration is also available.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Configuration</title>
